ation 4 — edge cases: empty mode-map, single-mode, registry drift, contextual defaults (thread 9)\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"content\": \"phase_main_loop: iteration 5 — contrarian steelman 'auto-default is fine' (thread 12)\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"content\": \"phase_synthesis: compile research.md + convergence report + final dashboard\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\"\n  }\n]","metadata":{"todos":[{"content":"phase_init: write config, state.jsonl, strategy, registry, dashboard to glm-max lineage dir","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_main_loop: iteration 1 — Layer-0<->Layer-1 advisor coupling (thread 2)","status":"in_progress","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_main_loop: iteration 2 — cross-hub generalization / detection-routed universal (thread 6)","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_main_loop: iteration 3 — second-order anti-patterns of null+mode-map (thread 7)","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_main_loop: iteration 4 — edge cases: empty mode-map, single-mode, registry drift, contextual defaults (thread 9)","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_main_loop: iteration 5 — contrarian steelman 'auto-default is fine' (thread 12)","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_synthesis: compile research.md + convergence report + final dashboard","status":"pending","priority":"high"}],"truncated":false},"title":"6 todos","time":{"start":1784313823203,"end":1784313823204}},"id":"prt_f71643fe10016MEquLtYBJa3Hq","sessionID":"ses_08ea082cdffeOdjcwgjfes92M1","messageID":"msg_f71640d37001pw39S777Z87UKG"}}
