{"type":"text","timestamp":1784313863565,"sessionID":"ses_08ea082cdffeOdjcwgjfes92M1","part":{"id":"prt_f7164d519001LO270dtkgkiztG","messageID":"msg_f716496ff001maq3PwMJMe5mHq","sessionID":"ses_08ea082cdffeOdjcwgjfes92M1","type":"text","text":"Critical evidence: the advisor already pre-resolves `system-deep-loop` modes (`--deep-skill-routing-json`, `MODE_REGISTRY_PATH` → system-deep-loop). This is a Layer-0↔Layer-1 coupling precedent. Let me confirm the deep-routing shape and the recommend return.","time":{"start":1784313861401,"end":1784313863564}}}
