{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784314221207,"sessionID":"ses_08ea082cdffeOdjcwgjfes92M1","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_7def58616b49437f8d4b4b16","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Research Dashboard — glm-max lineage\n\n**Lineage:** glm-max (cli-opencode / GLM-5.2) | **Mode:** research, divergent Run 2 | **Stop policy:** max-iterations (5)\n**Session:** fanout-glm-max-1784313510669-wn3vsj | **Started:** 2026-07-17T18:41:00Z\n\n> Convergence is telemetry only under `stopPolicy: max-iterations`. The loop runs all 5 iterations.\n\n## Iteration Table\n\n| run | focus | newInfoRatio | findings | status | thread |\n|-----|-------|--------------|----------|--------|--------|\n| 1 | Layer-0↔Layer-1 coupling under null defaultMode | 0.85 | 4 | complete | 2 |\n| 2 | detection-routed universal? sk-design feasibility | 0.80 | 4 | complete | 6 |\n\n## Question Status\n\n2/5 answered — **Q1, Q2 resolved.** Q3–Q5 open.\n\n- **Q1:** no re-escalation; defer terminates at user; advisor pre-resolves modes for one hub only.\n- **Q2:** detection-routed NOT universal (needs environmental signal); archetype is per-axis; sk-code is hybrid.\n\n## Convergence Trend\n\n- Ratios: 0.85 → 0.80 (slight descent as expected on divergent frontier).\n- Direction: still opening new territory; convergence is advisory only (max-iterations policy).\n\n## Dead Ends\n\n- \"null pushes cost to Layer-0\" — ruled out (iter 1).\n- \"all hubs converge on detection-routed\" — ruled out (iter 2): no environmental signal.\n\n## Blocked Stops\n\nNone (max-iterations policy).\n\n## Next Focus\n\nIteration 3 → Q3 (thread 7): second-order anti-patterns of null+mode-map. Does the fix recreate the original disease (mode-map-as-new-catch-all-bias)?\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0063-skilled-router-collapse/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/021-default-mode-policy-research/research/lineages/glm-max/deep-research-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0063-skilled-router-collapse/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/021-default-mode-policy-research/research/lineages/glm-max/deep-research-dashboard.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/021-default-mode-policy-research/research/lineages/glm-max/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1784314221201,"end":1784314221206}},"id":"prt_f716a5290001m9UJI9O3z9PTmd","sessionID":"ses_08ea082cdffeOdjcwgjfes92M1","messageID":"msg_f716a11d0001cuQLlyzCoLxAY0"}}
