{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784314895723,"sessionID":"ses_08ea082cdffeOdjcwgjfes92M1","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_5ecb63b6c5e44b97a1a44bf7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Research Dashboard — glm-max lineage (COMPLETE)\n\n**Lineage:** glm-max (cli-opencode / GLM-5.2) | **Mode:** research, divergent Run 2 | **Status:** complete\n**Stop reason:** `maxIterationsReached` (5/5; stopPolicy: max-iterations; convergence telemetry-only)\n**Session:** fanout-glm-max-1784313510669-wn3vsj | **Started:** 2026-07-17T18:41:00Z | **Synthesized:** 2026-07-17T19:08:00Z\n\n## Iteration Table\n\n| run | focus | newInfoRatio | findings | status | thread |\n|-----|-------|--------------|----------|--------|--------|\n| 1 | Layer-0↔Layer-1 coupling under null defaultMode | 0.85 | 4 | complete | 2 |\n| 2 | detection-routed universal? sk-design feasibility | 0.80 | 4 | complete | 6 |\n| 3 | second-order anti-patterns of null+mode-map | 0.70 | 5 | complete | 7 |\n| 4 | edge cases breaking the archetype rule | 0.75 | 4 | complete | 9 |\n| 5 | contrarian steelman: is auto-default fine? | 0.65 | 4 | complete | 12 |\n\n## Question Status\n\n**5/5 answered — ALL resolved.**\n\n- **Q1:** no re-escalation to Layer-0; defer terminates at user; advisor pre-resolves one hub only.\n- **Q2:** detection-routed NOT universal; archetype is per-axis; sk-code is hybrid.\n- **Q3:** 4 anti-patterns; canon names hub-identity-on-default; menu-vs-scorer split.\n- **Q4:** cli=detection-defaulted (distinct fourth shape); uniform flip-4 → 1+3 split; detection targets default axis; single-mode threshold.\n- **Q5:** falsifiable four-shape rule; cli recovered as detection-defaulted (the one disagreement); three nulls downgraded to directional-pending-measurement.\n\n## Convergence Trend\n\n- Ratios: 0.85 → 0.80 → 0.70 → 0.75 → 0.65 | **Average: 0.75**\n- Non-monotonic, modestly descending — consistent with a divergent frontier that broadened rather than converged. Final dip is expected (contrarian pass reassembles, not gathers).\n- Under max-iterations policy, novelty never triggered STOP. `entropyCoverage` reached 1.0 (all threads opened).\n\n## Dead Ends (Eliminated Alternatives)\n\n- \"null pushes cost to Layer-0\" — ruled out (iter 1).\n- \"all hubs converge on detection-routed\" — ruled out (iter 2).\n- \"loading smart_routing.md recreates bias\" — ruled out (iter 3).\n- \"all four flips encode identically\" — ruled out (iter 4).\n- \"categorical steelman: keep all five\" — ruled out (iter 5).\n- \"the three flips are proven\" — ruled out (iter 5: directional-pending-measurement).\n\n## Blocked Stops\n\nNone. Loop completed on maxIterationsReached.\n\n## Deliverable\n\n`research.md` — glm-max divergent synthesis: the falsifiable four-shape decision rule; the 1+3 per-hub split (cli = detection-defaulted, not null; three nulls confirmed-but-downgraded); the menu-vs-scorer fallback semantics split; drift-as-gate; single-mode canon threshold.\n\n## Next Step\n\nCross-lineage merge with sibling lineages (sol-ultra, luna-max, terra-max) is the operator's next step, not this lineage's. This lineage has converged independently.\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0063-skilled-router-collapse/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/021-default-mode-policy-research/research/lineages/glm-max/deep-research-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0063-skilled-router-collapse/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/021-default-mode-policy-research/research/lineages/glm-max/deep-research-dashboard.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/021-default-mode-policy-research/research/lineages/glm-max/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1784314895717,"end":1784314895722}},"id"